                A lot of people in our country believe that menstrual health and hygiene is not something that can be
                discussed quite openly. In fact a lot of people believe it to be a taboo , spoken about only in hushed
                tones. Thus, there is a high need to normalize this concept in the mindsets of the general public. Since
                proper education about this topic is not given in a lot of schools, girls are forced to learn about it
                from the internet from a huge variety of sources. Often they are afraid of asking any questions they
                might have regarding this to anyone. Our research in this matter showed the lack of a centralized system
                where people could get their doubts answered, get their myths busted, get professional help and so on.
                Thus, our goal is to create a system that not only gives the right information about menstrual health
